text: Zlatko Bužina (born 6 March 1966) is a Croatian rower. He competed in the men's coxless pair event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1966 births Category:Living people Category:Croatian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Croatia Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Zagreb
